90905, \"rank\": 9.224671645432753e-12, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World Rugby Chairman,Sir Bill Beaumontsaid: \\\"We are thrilled to unveil the rugby sevens Olympic pools \\u00a0for what promises to be an epic, coming-of-age tournament for our sport in the French capital.\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2148, \"end\": 2159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Rugby\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6660733989615183e-17, \"text\": \"World Rugby\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Rugby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Rugby\"}, {\"begin\": 2330, \"end\": 2336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.7801685196074803, \"rank\": 0.23808504122390056, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In one month's time, our sport will have the honour of kicking-off Paris 2024 in style with an exciting and spectacular brand of rugby that will excite the hundreds of thousands of fans in Stade de France and capture millions more hearts and minds of those watching around the world.\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2537, \"end\": 2552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Rugby sevens is a fantastic engine to grow our sport and on its third Olympic appearance is already proving to be one of the attractions of the Games with record enthusiasm for tickets, mouthwatering rivalries and two strong French national teams hoping to achieve their Olympic dreams on home soil.\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2859, \"end\": 2880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French national teams\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We know from Rugby World Cup 2023 what an amazing rugby show Paris can put on and the Olympic Games will be no different with knowledgeable and passionate fans expected to fill the stadium and create an incredible atmosphere for the players and teams to showcase their unique combination of speed, strength and sensational skills.\\\"\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 3267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2997, \"end\": 3002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3515112419682472e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics 2024 men's competition will take place from 24-27 July, with the women's tournament following on 28-30 July.\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's gold medal match on 27 July will see the first team sport gold medal of the Games awarded.\", \"from\": 3398, \"to\": 3498, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 3500, \"to\": 3579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3500, \"end\": 3503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999310631785343, \"rank\": 6.893800189628013e-05, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"